Happy holidays! Thanks everyone for your love and support over the past year. I’m especially grateful for my families (including Bubu and Gugu!) who would always be with me and love me unconditionally.  Because of them, I’m fearless to overcome any challenges. I wish everyone stays healthy and happy in the upcoming year, and moves one step closer to become the person we want to be. Happy New Year❤️

Also we thank @addictionpetfoods for providing us the grain-free Salmon Bleu cat food. They are made with Salmon in the ocean of New Zealand. Definitely check it out on Chewy.com.
